cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image-to-image transformation and visual recognition tasks. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a model based on generative adversarial networks. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with generating images with correct identity labels, which is a challenging task in AI. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with image transformation tasks with large deformation in poses, viewpoints or scales. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with generating new images while preserving the identity of the input image, which is relevant to multimedia applications.
